Tag: V00-00-02	
2012-02-22 Mikhail S. Dubrovin
- This version has fully functional plots for 
	1. spectrum in rect
	2. zoom in rect
	3. profile along the line
	4. x-y projections of zoomed rect rigion with spectum
	5. r-phi projections of the wedge rigion with spectum
	6. center for wedge
	
- Adding a new type of plot for XXX
	For GUI:
	--------
	1. copy ImgGUISpectrum.py -> ImgGUIXXX.py (edit)
        2. add all necessary calls in ImgGUI.py (edit)
        3. add necessary configuration parameters in ImgConfigParameters.py (edit)
	4. ImgDrawOnTop.py    (edit for new geometry forms only)
	5. ImgDrawOutside.py  (edit)
	6. ImgDrawSpectrum.py -> ImgDrawXXX.py (edit)

